      "span_text": "One of these common single nucleotide polymorphisms (SNPs) in the AUTS2 gene is rs6943555, which comprises a single nucleotide change of T to A in intron 4.  Schumann et al.  reported that the A allele of rs6943555 significantly increases AUTS2 gene expression in the prefrontal cortex of the human brain compared with the T allele."
